Author: Carsten Urbach [aut, cre], Bartosz Kostrzewa [aut], Johann Ostmeyer [aut], Martin Ueding [aut] 
Maintainer: Carsten Urbach <urbach@hiskp.uni-bonn.de>
SystemRequirements: Gnu Scientific Library version >= 1.8
Description: Toolkit to extract hadronic quantities from Lattice Quantum Chromodynamics simulations (see e.g. ETM Collaboration, P. Boucaud et al. (2008) <https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cpc.2008.06.013>). It contains functionality for IO, plotting, bootstrap and jackknife resampling, fitting, generalised eigenvalue problem solving (see e.g. B. Blossier et al. (2009) <https://doi.org/10.1088/1126-6708/2009/04/094> and M. Fischer et al. (2020) <https://inspirehep.net/literature/1792113>), error and autocorrelation estimation as well as other areas.
